2014-06-16  Fritz Reese  <Reese-Fritz@zai.com>

	* resolve.c (build_default_init_expr): Move core to public function
	in expr.c.
	* expr.c (gfc_build_default_init_expr): New public version of
	build_default_init_expr from resolve.c. Takes only a typespec and
	locus instead of a symbol.
	* gfortran.h: Declare gfc_build_default_init_expr.
	* decl.c: Use gfc_build_default_init_expr in conjunction with
	-finit-struct and other -finit-* to initialize structure members
	automatically.

2014-06-11  Fritz Reese  <Reese-Fritz@zai.com>

	* gfortran.h: Add flag_init_derived for -finit-derived.
	* invoke.texi: Describe -finit-derived.
	* lang.opt: Add -finit-derived option.
	* options.c: Set gfc_option.flag_init_derived when switched on.


